    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No Way Home: <i>BLAMMO!</i> is a <strong>tactical arcade roguelite</strong> that's all about fast-paced  twin stick space combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every run is a new adventure. Tinker with your ship, experiment with unique weapons, and discover interesting new builds as you blast your way through waves of enemies and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246120/extras/5a1b8f906cb8c433f2df79ea97bbd41c.poster.avif?t=1733447955\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246120/extras/5a1b8f906cb8c433f2df79ea97bbd41c.webm?t=1733447955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246120/extras/5a1b8f906cb8c433f2df79ea97bbd41c.mp4?t=1733447955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The gameplay is simple!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a Loadout</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start BLAMMING!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Salvage, Tinker, Upgrade</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BLAM HARDER!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Die | Win</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new co-pilots, their perks, and other long-form progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GO AGAIN!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246120/extras/123b9301348efe451f672de43012013e.poster.avif?t=1733447955\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246120/extras/123b9301348efe451f672de43012013e.webm?t=1733447955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246120/extras/123b9301348efe451f672de43012013e.mp4?t=1733447955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>BLAMMO!</strong></i><strong> Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique hand-drawn world </strong>of<strong> </strong><u>Scott Vanden Bosch.</u></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple ship, co-pilot loadouts</strong> to experiment with.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Handcrafted x procedural levels</strong> providing endless fun.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Massive bosses</strong> of all shapes and sizes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tactical gameplay</strong>. This isn't just a point and shoot.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>More to be announced!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Editor's note: This is where I've been told by the designers to stop asking for stuff as they are constantly adding and experimenting!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Why Early Access?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SMG has been heads down on larger titles under NDA for the last 3 years and we’re using this game as a release valve to have fun with open development with the community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We’re excited to hear feedback, ideas, and thoughts as we continue to shape BLAMMO! into the ultimate roguelite experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meet Cho &amp; Matey</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246120/extras/e78e131e2fba7a143a549b8d409b179b.avif?t=1733447955\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246120/extras_big/e78e131e2fba7a143a549b8d409b179b.avif?t=1733447955 width=800 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cho is now seeking fame and fortune with her sassy talking AI companion Matey along for the ride.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cho seeks out <i><strong>The Monolith</strong></i>, a reconfiguring multi-room box of danger, mystery, enemies and LOOT! to claim the biggest haul ever, <i><strong>The Key To The Universe</strong></i><strong>.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>New Ships</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We want new ships to be a constant surprise for players. Keep playing to unlock more unique starter loadouts and configurations and explore deeper into customisations that change the way you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246120/extras/0927790f408117583e1efc7f3301b729.avif?t=1733447955\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246120/extras_big/0927790f408117583e1efc7f3301b729.avif?t=1733447955 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>New Weapons &amp; Ship Upgrades</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We’re in the fun stage of building out the weapons &amp; ship upgrades, upgrading them from the first game and discovering fun new combinations for players to BLAM! with.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
